---
// Interactive onboarding guide - standalone page, no sidebar
// docs.hebbs.ai/guide/
---
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Get Started with HEBBS</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Install, index, recall, tune. A step-by-step interactive guide to HEBBS." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-snap-type: y proximity; }
    body {
      background: #0a0a0b;
      color: #d4d4d8;
      font-family: "Inter", ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    ::selection { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3); }

    /* ── Stage layout ── */
    .stage {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 80px 24px;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .stage-inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── Typography ── */
    .stage-num {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #f59e0b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ededef;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    /* ── Terminal ── */
    .terminal {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .terminal-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e20;
    }
    .terminal-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .terminal-dot.r { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.5); }
    .terminal-dot.y { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.5); }
    .terminal-dot.g { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.4); }
    .terminal-title { margin-left: 8px; font-size: 11px; color: #3f3f46; }
    .terminal-body { padding: 20px 24px; overflow-x: auto; }
    .terminal-body pre { white-space: pre; }

    /* Terminal colors */
    .t-prompt { color: #f59e0b; }
    .t-cmd { color: #ededef; }
    .t-flag { color: #67e8f9; }
    .t-str { color: #34d399; }
    .t-out { color: #8a8a8e; }
    .t-num { color: #f59e0b; }
    .t-dim { color: #3f3f46; }
    .t-pass { color: #34d399; }
    .t-fail { color: #f87171; }
    .t-warn { color: #fbbf24; }

    /* ── Provider tabs ── */
    .provider-tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .provider-tab {
      padding: 6px 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      background: transparent;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .provider-tab:hover { border-color: #3f3f46; color: #d4d4d8; }
    .provider-tab.active { border-color: #f59e0b; color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.06); }
    .provider-cmd { display: none; }
    .provider-cmd.active { display: block; }

    /* ── Recall demo cards ── */
    .recall-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .recall-card {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .recall-card:hover { border-color: #3f3f46; }
    .recall-card.active { border-color: #f59e0b; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.03); }
    .recall-card .query-label {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .recall-card .query-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #ededef;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .recall-card .query-flags {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #3f3f46;
    }
    .recall-card .query-flags .flag { color: #67e8f9; }
    .recall-result {
      margin-top: 16px;
      display: none;
    }
    .recall-card.active .recall-result { display: block; }

    /* ── Scorecard ── */
    .scorecard {
      display: grid;
      gap: 4px;
    }
    .score-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr 60px 60px;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .score-row.header {
      color: #3f3f46;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .score-row.pass { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.05); }
    .score-row.fail { background: rgba(248,113,113,0.05); }
    .score-row .qnum { color: #3f3f46; }
    .score-row .qtext { color: #8a8a8e; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
    .score-row .before { text-align: right; }
    .score-row .after { text-align: right; }

    /* ── Result banner ── */
    .result-banner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      background: rgba(245,158,11,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.15);
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .result-num {
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .result-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .result-arrow { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 24px; }
    .result-desc { flex: 1; font-size: 14px; color: #8a8a8e; line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── Rules file preview ── */
    .rules-file {
      background: #141415;
      border: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .rules-file-header {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e20;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #3f3f46;
    }
    .rules-file-body {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #8a8a8e;
    }
    .rules-file-body .heading { color: #f59e0b; font-weight: 600; }
    .rules-file-body .rule { color: #d4d4d8; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .cta-primary { background: #f59e0b; color: #0a0a0b; }
    .cta-primary:hover { background: #fbbf24; }
    .cta-secondary { border: 1px solid #1e1e20; color: #8a8a8e; }
    .cta-secondary:hover { border-color: #3f3f46; color: #d4d4d8; }

    /* ── Navigation dots ── */
    .nav-dots {
      position: fixed;
      right: 24px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #1e1e20;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .nav-dot.active { background: #f59e0b; transform: scale(1.3); }
    .nav-dot:hover { background: #3f3f46; }

    /* ── Back to docs ── */
    .back-link {
      position: fixed;
      top: 20px;
      left: 24px;
      z-index: 100;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #3f3f46;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .back-link:hover { color: #8a8a8e; }

    /* ── Copy button ── */
    .copy-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 12px;
      right: 12px;
      background: #1e1e20;
      border: 1px solid #3f3f46;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #8a8a8e;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .copy-btn:hover { color: #ededef; border-color: #8a8a8e; }

    /* ── Fade-in animation ── */
    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease-out, transform 0.7s ease-out;
    }
    .fade-up.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .stage { padding: 60px 16px; }
      .terminal-body { padding: 16px; font-size: 11px; }
      .result-banner { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
      .nav-dots { display: none; }
      .score-row { grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr 48px 48px; font-size: 10px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; docs</a>

  <nav class="nav-dots" id="nav-dots">
    <button class="nav-dot active" data-stage="0" title="Install"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="1" title="Set Up"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="2" title="Recall"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="3" title="Panel"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="4" title="Tune"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="5" title="Learn"></button>
    <button class="nav-dot" data-stage="6" title="Start"></button>
  </nav>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- STAGE 1: Install                                                -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="stage" id="stage-0">
    <div class="stage-inner fade-up">
      <div class="stage-num">Step 1</div>
      <h2>Install HEBBS</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">One binary. No dependencies. No services to run.</p>

      <div class="terminal" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <span class="terminal-dot r"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot y"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot g"></span>
          <span class="terminal-title">terminal</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <pre><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">brew install hebbs-ai/tap/hebbs</span>

<span class="t-out">==&gt; Downloading hebbs-0.3.1.tar.gz</span>
<span class="t-out">==&gt; Installing hebbs</span>
<span class="t-pass">&#10003; hebbs installed successfully</span>

<span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs --version</span>
<span class="t-out">hebbs 0.3.1</span></pre>
        </div>
        <button class="copy-btn" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('brew install hebbs-ai/tap/hebbs')">copy</button>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 16px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #3f3f46;">
        or: <span style="color: #8a8a8e; cursor: pointer;" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('curl -sSf https://hebbs.ai/install | sh')">curl -sSf https://hebbs.ai/install | sh</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- STAGE 2: Set Up (init + index)                                  -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="stage" id="stage-1">
    <div class="stage-inner fade-up">
      <div class="stage-num">Step 2</div>
      <h2>Point it at your project</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Pick your LLM provider. HEBBS handles embedding, extraction, and indexing.</p>

      <div class="provider-tabs" id="provider-tabs">
        <button class="provider-tab active" data-provider="openai">OpenAI</button>
        <button class="provider-tab" data-provider="anthropic">Anthropic</button>
        <button class="provider-tab" data-provider="gemini">Gemini</button>
        <button class="provider-tab" data-provider="ollama">Ollama (local)</button>
      </div>

      <div class="terminal" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <span class="terminal-dot r"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot y"></span>
          <span class="terminal-dot g"></span>
          <span class="terminal-title">~/projects/legal-docs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div class="provider-cmd active" data-provider="openai">
            <pre><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs init</span> <span class="t-flag">--provider</span> <span class="t-str">openai</span> <span class="t-flag">--key</span> <span class="t-str">$OPENAI_API_KEY</span>

<span class="t-out">  Created .hebbs/config.toml</span>
<span class="t-out">  Provider: openai (gpt-4o-mini)</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedding: text-embedding-3-small</span>
<span class="t-out">  Daemon started (pid 48201)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  Ready.</span>

<span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs index</span>

<span class="t-out">  Scanning 52 files...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Extracting propositions (10 parallel)...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedded 949 memories (3.1s)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  &#10003; 52 files, 465 sections, 484 propositions</span></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="provider-cmd" data-provider="anthropic">
            <pre><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs init</span> <span class="t-flag">--provider</span> <span class="t-str">anthropic</span> <span class="t-flag">--key</span> <span class="t-str">$ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</span>

<span class="t-out">  Created .hebbs/config.toml</span>
<span class="t-out">  Provider: anthropic (claude-haiku-4-5)</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedding: text-embedding-3-small (OpenAI key required)</span>
<span class="t-out">  Daemon started (pid 48201)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  Ready.</span>

<span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs index</span>

<span class="t-out">  Scanning 52 files...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Extracting propositions (10 parallel)...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedded 949 memories (3.4s)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  &#10003; 52 files, 465 sections, 484 propositions</span></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="provider-cmd" data-provider="gemini">
            <pre><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs init</span> <span class="t-flag">--provider</span> <span class="t-str">gemini</span> <span class="t-flag">--key</span> <span class="t-str">$GEMINI_API_KEY</span>

<span class="t-out">  Created .hebbs/config.toml</span>
<span class="t-out">  Provider: gemini (gemini-2.0-flash)</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedding: text-embedding-004</span>
<span class="t-out">  Daemon started (pid 48201)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  Ready.</span>

<span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs index</span>

<span class="t-out">  Scanning 52 files...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Extracting propositions (10 parallel)...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedded 949 memories (2.8s)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  &#10003; 52 files, 465 sections, 484 propositions</span></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="provider-cmd" data-provider="ollama">
            <pre><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs init</span> <span class="t-flag">--provider</span> <span class="t-str">ollama</span>

<span class="t-out">  Created .hebbs/config.toml</span>
<span class="t-out">  Provider: ollama (qwen3:4b)</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedding: local ONNX (EmbeddingGemma-300M)</span>
<span class="t-out">  Daemon started (pid 48201)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  Ready. No API key needed.</span>

<span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">hebbs index</span>

<span class="t-out">  Scanning 52 files...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Extracting propositions (local)...</span>
<span class="t-out">  Embedded 949 memories (8.2s)</span>
<span class="t-pass">  &#10003; 52 files, 465 sections, 484 propositions</span></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- STAGE 3: First Recall                                           -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="stage" id="stage-2">
    <div class="stage-inner fade-up">
      <div class="stage-num">Step 3</div>
      <h2>Ask it anything</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Same memories. Different strategies. Click a query to see the results.</p>

      <div class="recall-cards" id="recall-cards">
        <div class="recall-card active" data-query="0">
          <div class="query-label" style="color: #f59e0b;">Similarity</div>
          <div class="query-text">"What's our ransomware coverage limit?"</div>
          <div class="query-flags"><span class="flag">--strategy</span> similarity <span class="flag">-k</span> 5</div>
          <div class="recall-result">
            <div class="terminal" style="margin-top: 12px;">
              <div class="terminal-body" style="padding: 14px 18px;">
                <pre><span class="t-out">#  Score   Source                              Content</span>
<span class="t-num">1</span>  <span class="t-pass">0.89</span>   <span class="t-str">cyber-insurance-policy.md</span>       Coverage: $2M per incident
<span class="t-num">2</span>  <span class="t-pass">0.86</span>   <span class="t-str">endorsement-ransomware.md</span>      Ransomware Payment Sublimit: $500K
<span class="t-num">3</span>  <span class="t-warn">0.71</span>   <span class="t-str">risk-register-2025-q2.md</span>       RISK-007: Insurance coverage gap
<span class="t-dim">   3 results in 4ms</span></pre>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="recall-card" data-query="1">
          <div class="query-label" style="color: #67e8f9;">Temporal</div>
          <div class="query-text">"How has the Cloudvault risk rating changed?"</div>
          <div class="query-flags"><span class="flag">--strategy</span> temporal <span class="flag">--entity-id</span> cloudvault</div>
          <div class="recall-result">
            <div class="terminal" style="margin-top: 12px;">
              <div class="terminal-body" style="padding: 14px 18px;">
                <pre><span class="t-out">#  Date         Source                           Content</span>
<span class="t-num">1</span>  <span class="t-dim">2024-10</span>  <span class="t-str">vendor-risk-cloudvault.md</span>      85% concentration, MEDIUM risk
<span class="t-num">2</span>  <span class="t-dim">2024-Q4</span>  <span class="t-str">risk-register-2024-q4.md</span>      RISK-001: Cloudvault (HIGH)
<span class="t-num">3</span>  <span class="t-dim">2025-Q2</span>  <span class="t-str">risk-register-2025-q2.md</span>      RISK-001: now MEDIUM (EU deploy)
<span class="t-dim">   3 results in 2ms (timeline order)</span></pre>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="recall-card" data-query="2">
          <div class="query-label" style="color: #34d399;">Causal</div>
          <div class="query-text">"Why was the insurance coverage gap flagged?"</div>
          <div class="query-flags"><span class="flag">--strategy</span> causal <span class="flag">--max-depth</span> 4</div>
          <div class="recall-result">
            <div class="terminal" style="margin-top: 12px;">
              <div class="terminal-body" style="padding: 14px 18px;">
                <pre><span class="t-out">Causal chain (4 hops):</span>

<span class="t-str">cyber-insurance-policy.md</span>  Coverage: $2M per incident
  <span class="t-dim">&#8595; caused_by</span>
<span class="t-str">endorsement-ransomware.md</span>  Sublimit overrides to $500K
  <span class="t-dim">&#8595; caused_by</span>
<span class="t-str">insurance-review.md</span>        Board told $2M, actual $500K
  <span class="t-dim">&#8595; caused_by</span>
<span class="t-str">risk-register-2025-q2.md</span>   RISK-007: Coverage gap (NEW)
<span class="t-dim">   4 hops in 6ms</span></pre>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- STAGE 4: Memory Palace                                          -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="stage" id="stage-3">
    <div class="stage-inner fade-up">
      <div class="stage-num">Step 4</div>
      <h2>See your brain</h2>
